+# SwapOnBase notes
+
+Picked Uniswap V3 on Base.
+
+The contract uses Base's Uniswap SwapRouter02 at `0x2626664c2603336E57B271c5C0b26F421741e481` and swaps through the USDC/WETH 0.05% pool. I picked Uniswap V3 because USDC/WETH is one of its deepest, most actively traded Base pairs, and the concentrated-liquidity 0.05% pool is the canonical low-fee route for this stablecoin-to-WETH swap.
